"Awsome" JetV said allowed.  "Lets go get him Artemis."

All of a sudden a large hand grapsed JetV's shoulder.  "No JetV.  I 
will get him" came a voice from Crotale.  He looked over to Pacifix, 
not caring if PAcifix cared or not.  Then walking out he began to 
transform into his own helicopter mode.  His large bubble sattelite 
from above his rotor showing him clearly where this signal was coming 
from.  He warmed up his blades as he hummed off the ground slowly.

Repugnus looked to PAcifix.  "Sure thing.  After that I'll give you a 
full body wax there chief." he said smugly.  The slumoing off and 
changing to his beast mode running off thrguh the bush letting his 
vision sensors guide him.
